playstore_details.description:
Learn Bitcoin, Cryptocurrency & Blockchain for Free with Crypto School!
Crypto School is changing the way people learn & start making money in the Cryptocurrency market!
• It’s free, for real.
• It’s fun. Are you bored at reading crypto guides or tutorials? NOT ANYMORE!
• It’s effective. Enjoy the learning by reading bite-sized lessons followed by review questions.
Reading, Learning and Enjoying ANYTIME & ANYWHERE without the Internet connection!
